org.bukkit.potion

Interface PotionDataHolder

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AreaEffectCloud, PotionMeta, TippedArrow

    public interface PotionDataHolder
    A mutable object that has fields for color, base potion data and custom effects, like a PotionMeta, but is not necessarily an ItemMeta.
